headline: Why Centene (CNC) Is Up 9.8% After Trump’s Proposed ACA Subsidy Extension and What’s Next
summary: In late November 2025, reports confirmed that President Donald Trump would propose a two-year extension to the Affordable Care Act’s premium subsidies, alongside new income eligibility levels and minimum premium payment requirements. This development is particularly significant for Centene, which relies on the ACA marketplace for commercial growth and has credited subsidy extensions with helping drive its expansion and recent financial guidance.
